      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this superlative example, maintained to an exacting standard that mirrors its original showroom delivery. This vehicle exhibits a flawless aesthetic and mechanical profile, suited for the most fastidious collector. Every detail, from the pristine cabin appointments to the mirror-finish exterior, underscores a legacy of meticulous stewardship. This is an investment-grade acquisition for those who demand uncompromising quality and performance.",
