      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I am honestly so excited to show you this beauty. It is in absolutely pristine, showroom-level condition\u2014I've pampered it from day one and it truly looks and drives like it just rolled off the lot! If you've been looking for that perfect, 'like-new' feel without the brand-new price tag, you've found it. Come by and see it for yourself, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43500.0,
